General Information
===================

Python converter module for the accelerator code TRANSPORT.
It can convert TRANSPORT input into MAD and GMAD (BDSIM) lattices.
It can read TRANSPORT output into Python lists, which can be used standalone or with the module pybdsim.

Written by Will Shields

Currently maintained and developed by:

Will Shields          <william.shields.2010@live.rhul.ac.uk>
Jochem Snuverink      <jochem.snuverink@psi.ch>

Basic Commands
==============

# Convert TRANSPORT input
from pytransport import convert
convert.pytransport('FOR001.DAT')

# Read TRANSPORT output
from pytransport import reader
a = reader.reader()
data = a.get_data('FOR002.DAT')
